<br>
<br>
Quote:<br>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
 After asking &quot;am I worthy&quot; for the 3rd time yesterday after a mess of faction work I got frustrated and started off from the start again...<br>
<br>
To my surprise, even though I am not yet worthy (buggy #$%# quest) I was able to get more information from the remains :<br>
<br>
What is Vex Thal <br>
<br>
The city of shadow is sealed by powerful magic. Only one who wears the Talisman of Akelha Ra can pass through the seals of the gate. <br>
<br>
What talisman of akelha ra? <br>
<br>
This medallion was a piece of the talisman shattered long ago by the storm that swept through the maiden's eye. You must first find the ten silver links that were once attached to the talisman. They lie scattered throughout all of Luclin. Return the talisman to me when you have reunited the medallion with the scattered links. <br>
<br>
<br>
He hands you a &quot;Medallion&quot; which is a 10 slot tiny box with a combine button (he hands it to you open so you have to camp to close it the first time). Looks like its VP key all over again....<br>
<br>
Everyone try and find the 10 silver links! <br>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
It would be nice if the 10 seals were combined in this container, but according to the stories given, they aren't really related. Shattered Seals of Warding are not silver links. They are found in one zone, not scattered throughout Luclin.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ulifty.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lifty</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/18/01 8:28:28 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3424.topic&index=127>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Shattered Seal of Warding - Shissar Temple Quest</span><hr size=1> there is a taskmaster in echo caverns all by his lonesome (well, except for the skellies he commands).  haven't got him to drop a seal yet tho, only some crap items. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#FF0000>- </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse>The Safehouse</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13>Quests of Norrath</a> <font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href="http://www.thesafehouse.org">The Safehouse website</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font> <center><a href="http://www.guildboss.com"><img
